"        \tclients can customize files such as /etc/modules.conf, /etc/"
"sysconfig/mouse, \n"
"        \t/etc/sysconfig/keyboard on a per-client basis.\n"
"\n"
"        Note: Enabling local client hardware configuration does enable root "
